{"tid":758301,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"費格遜腦部手術後首露面　感謝醫護人員治療","createTime":"2018-07-27T14:24:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-27T16:55:13.000Z","uid":41423,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"5002a1f4593179a715f08c6698bf1765eff9e655","tid":758301,"uid":41423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T14:24:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/sport/football/44971812\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fsport%2Ffootball%2F44971812&d=Dof9DDvoUSP8Q9BL3XsNpARJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=52e84503\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fsport%2Ffootball%2F44971812&h=51f8a0f9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/sport/football/44971812</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1409108_1_20180726225603.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1409108_1_20180726225603.jpg&h=d344d76b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1409108-20180726.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1409108-20180726.htm&d=Dof9DDvoUSP8Q9BL3XsNpARJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=647076fb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1409108-20180726.htm&h=8c95d3b5\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1409108-20180726.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n曼聯前領隊費格遜在5月完成腦部手術後首次透過視頻片段，感謝醫護人員救他一命。<br />\n<br />\n76歲的費格遜，在5月初因為急性腦出血，被送往索爾福德一間醫院做手術。費格遜在曼聯球會官方頻道的片段中，感謝各方的祝福與支持，並表示稍後會觀看曼聯新球季的比賽。<br />\n<br />\n朗尼、雲達沙等前曼聯球員亦在Twitter，表示高興見到費格遜康復進度良好。"},{"pid":"ec81ded6e978ef2bf4d527265dea6ba531ceac58","tid":758301,"uid":46904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T14:26:21.000Z","msg":"個樣唔同哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ebe855d439b6816837e141137e34721818e5f30","tid":7